{
  "stem": "15732.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I came out from the last, my father and my mother were standing on the-- there, waiting, with that particular young man that I call the leader of the group, with that particular young man because he worked it out that if I am not a stupid girl, then I'm going to come somehow to Linz to-- to the station.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said, you just wait here with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we will see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If she will not come, then we will then see what we can organize.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you wouldn't believe it, but two hours later we were taken with the car-- truck to Linz refugee camp that was starting to organize.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there were already groups there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And two hours later, I was dancing a hora with-- with all the others, forgotten what it-- that means to be young.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That is the benefit of being young and being enthusiastic and wanting to live.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had such a-- I had all those years of hiding, of war, of that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was so much [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] suppressed in that, that when it came the end of the-- all I wanted is to go on living and to catch up all those things that I-- that I missed.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in Linz, I remember that we were-- I was at my birthday, I was, means that was the 16th of November.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "20.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 20 then already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, 20 already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Linz, we were taken again with the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were no more borders, no more question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're taken to Munchen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Munchen, we were in that Deutsche Museum, Munchen Deutsches Museum.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there again we were registered.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
